cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper discusses attacks on deep learning systems, which are commonly used in computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The attacks specifically target face recognition systems (cs.CV) and use data poisoning strategies (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the importance of defense strategies (cs.SI) against these attacks.
